title: SwifTEA: We Unlocked The Vault!
description:
Taylor did it again! She threw words at us, had us unscramble them and post pics using that Red filter. What did we figure out? And most importantly, WHAT DOES THIS MEAN FOR US?
Big news. and we are super convinced that this can only mean one thing!
Plus, Simone Biles sweetness and proof that the scarf thief is indeed a dirty boy.
